# Life OS Monorepo

**Canonical repo:** `Ken-pan/life-os` at `/Users/kenpan/「Projects」/life-os`

| App | Path | Workspace name | Netlify site |
|-----|------|----------------|--------------|
| Planner | `apps/planner` | `planner-os` | planneros-ken |
| Fitness | `apps/fitness` | `fitness-os` | kens-fitnessos |
| Finance | `apps/finance` | `finance-os` | kensfinanceos |
| Music | `apps/music` | `music-os` | kens-musicos |

Shared: `packages/theme` (`@life-os/theme`), `packages/sync` (`@life-os/sync`).

## Commands (repo root)

```bash
npm install
npm run build          # turbo — all apps
npm run build:planner  # single app
cd apps/planner && npm run dev
```

## Do not

- Edit legacy archived repos (`planner-os`, `fitness-os`, `Moneymoneymoney`, `MusicOS`, `life-os-theme`, `life-os-sync`).
- Add `file:../life-os-theme` or vendored `packages/life-os-*` in this monorepo.
- Put nested `.github/workflows` under `apps/*` — CI lives at repo root.

## Deploy

Push `master` → Netlify Git build (path ignore per app). Docs: `docs/NETLIFY.md`, `docs/CANONICAL.md`.
